---
Format: Verse
By: Rainer Maria Rilke
Source:
  - Title: A Year with Rilke
    Editor:
      - Anita Barrows
      - Joanna Macy
    Page: 20
  - Title: The Book of Hours
    Location: II 3
Title: Am I Not the Whole?
Description: January 28
---
God, are you then the All? And I the separated one
who tumbles and rages?
Am I not the whole? Am I not all things
when I weep, and you the single one, who hears it?
